# EXPLAIN
"I built an automated server maintenance system using Ansible. The playbook performs system updates, disk and memory checks, and automatically creates backups of important directories. It also performs a conditional reboot only if updates require it. I scheduled the maintenance using Cron so the automation runs weekly without manual intervention. The solution helps maintain server health, improve reliability, and reduce manual operational effort."


